      <p>You can declare it as a gift but the risk will be that of ascertaining the value if the package is lost/damaged. </p>
<p>Or you can break up the $400 worth of package into smaller packages each under $400. That's how I do it, I buy two packages of books monthly, and each package is under $400 (inclusive of shipping charges).</p>
